\begin_inset Formula $\langle d\phi_{p}(v),d\phi_{p}(w)\rangle=\langle v,w\rangle$
\end_inset

, es decir, tal que 
\begin_inset Formula $d\phi_{p}:T_{p}S_{1}\to T_{\phi(p)}S_{2}$
